      <h2 class="text-center">Meet Our Team</h2>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="rounded-circle mb-3" alt="Team Member 1">
          <h5>John Doe</h5>
          <p class="text-muted">CEO</p>
          <p>John is the visionary leader of our company with over 20 years of experience in the industry.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="rounded-circle mb-3" alt="Team Member 2">
          <h5>Jane Smith</h5>
          <p class="text-muted">CTO</p>
          <p>Jane is the technical mastermind behind our innovative solutions and cutting-edge technology.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
          <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/150" class="rounded-circle mb-3" alt="Team Member 3">
          <h5>Bob Johnson</h5>
          <p class="text-muted">COO</p>
          <p>Bob ensures our operations run smoothly and efficiently, bringing exceptional organizational skills.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="bg-dark text-white text-center py-3">
    <div class="container">
      <p>&copy; 2024 Your Company. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>

